message.body: Hey Ang, I will not be coming to Starry Skies this time. I'm so sad about that but I think it's for the best. I am finishing up my antibiotics and hopefully pooping out the (dead) bodies of all the giardias in me but I am really depleted and need to stay
Dang. Im sorry to hear youre depleted,but glad its working itself out. Dont think im going to maine either,things taking all kindsa turns. I agree we sho
uld talk- soon,when are you free?
Thanks Ange. I'm here all day today and tomorrow so call whenever you want in general! I would love to hear your voice.
